  "keyFeatures": [
    "Import data from CSV, TSV, Excel, JSON, XML, RDF, and more",
    "Faceted browsing and filtering to explore large datasets",
    "Clustering algorithms to find and merge inconsistent values",
    "GREL expression language for powerful data transformations",
    "Reconciliation against external databases including Wikidata",
    "Full operation history with undo/redo support",
    "Export to CSV, Excel, JSON, RDF, SQL, and custom templates",
    "Extension system supporting Wikibase, Database, Jython, and PC-Axis",
    "Runs locally in the browser — your data never leaves your machine"
